def metric(y_actual,y_pred):
    r2=r2_score(y_actual,y_pred)
    RMSE=np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_actual,y_pred))
    print("R2 Score: {} | RMSE: {}".format(round(r2,2),round(RMSE,2)))
